            <para>
              <text>This section amends the Local Government Act 1974.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 319 is amended by adding the following subsection as subsection (2):</text>
              <amend quote="1">
                <subprov skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="yes" denominator="yes" quote="1">2</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>Before exercising a power under this section to do anything that will or is likely to interfere with any pipe, line, or other work associated with the supply of water, electricity, gas, or telecommunications, the council must give not less than 10 working days' notice in writing of the proposed interference to the owner of the pipe, line, or other work.</text>
